Dory Funk https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dory_Funk 0 Dorrance Wilhelm Funk (May 4, 1919 – June 3, 1973) was an American professional wrestler. He is the father of wrestlers Dory Funk Jr. and Terry Funk, and was the promoter of the Amarillo, Texas-based Western States Sports promotion.
